ral tens of hours, there are also over 20 side routes and quests featuring different stories and characters to explore. Join forces with diverse Illuminators as companions, cultivate relationships, and earn adventure rewards!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143680/extras/7611a802a2cba9353f2ab6fccf8378ba.avif?t=1772681622\" width=562 height=73 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143680/extras/1a9e8f486e1b9892cc974274c538c049.poster.avif?t=1772681622\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143680/extras/1a9e8f486e1b9892cc974274c538c049.webm?t=1772681622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143680/extras/1a9e8f486e1b9892cc974274c538c049.mp4?t=1772681622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The friendships and blessings you harvest along the journey will strengthen you in battle. Feel free to combine the \"Blessing Petals\" that are embedded with features of different characters to customize your battle style. In addition, there are many other well-designed cultivation systems that are ready for you to explore!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143680/extras/24a304828cad90dc954d192d25761af8.avif?t=1772681622\" width=615 height=345 /></span>",
